('adcb9deae73557006a8ac748f45288b4', '<div class="product_title_big">\r\n<h2>Helm AHM 5000</h2></div>\r\n<div>Ein Klassiker unter den Wassersporthelmen. Hochwertiges Finish und perfekte Optik. </div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><strong>Features:</strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>schlagfeste Schale<br />\r\n</li>\r\n<li>geprüfter CE 1385 Standard</li>\r\n<li>individuell verstellbar<br />\r\n</li>\r\n<li> Schaumpolster<br />\r\n</li></ul></div>\r\n<div><strong>Größen:</strong><br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Einheitsgröße<br />\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Polstereinlagen in den Größen S, M und L im Lieferumfang enthalten<br />\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Kopfumfang (min/max)<br />\r\n         53,34 - 60,32cm</li></ul></div>', '<div class="product_title_big">\r\n<h2>Shred Ready AHM 5000</h2></div>\r\n<div>"Plastic price without the plastic\r\nlook and feel. That''s what makes this new line so appealing...The\r\ngraphics make the helmet look like a more expensive carbon or composite\r\nmodel..." - Paddler Magazine, July/Aug 2000.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><strong>Features:</strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Hard ABS abrasion resistant shell</li>\r\n<li>CE 1385 Standard; International Standard for whitewater headgear.</li>\r\n<li>Faux Carbon Graphic., and Solid Colors</li>\r\n<li>Soft tubed nylon webbing</li>\r\n<li>Removable Compression Molded Ear Flaps</li>\r\n<li>Stainless steel rivets and burrs to stop the corrosion</li>\r\n<li>Easily adjustable four-point retention system</li>\r\n<li>Dura-Flex fastners, adjusters, and stops</li></ul></div>\r\n<div><strong>Sizes:</strong><br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>One Size<br />\r\n             Small, Medium and Large fitting pads are included with each helmet for a custom fit</li>\r\n<li>Head Circumference (min/max)<br />\r\n         21'''' - 23 3/4''''<br />\r\n         53,34 - 60,32cm<br />\r\n</li></ul></div>\r\n<p><font size="3"><span>To determine your head circumference, simply\r\nmeasure the circumference of your head at the widest part. Shred Ready\r\nhelmets are engineered to fit a wide range of head sizes.</span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p></p>', '', '', 'kiteboarding,kite,helm,protection,sicherheit', 'kiteboarding,kite,helmet,protection,sicherheit', '', ''),
('adc5ee42bd3c37a27a488769d22ad9ed', '<div class="product_title_big">\r\n<h2>NPX Vamp Semidry 5/4/3 GBL 2010</h2></div>\r\n<div class="product_text3">\r\n<div>Wie der Cult für Männer, ist der\r\nVamp ein preiswerter Neoprenanzug für Frauen, der trotzdem den NPX\r\nAnsprüchen gerecht wird. Ein auffälliges Design soll vor allem auch die\r\njüngere Generation ansprechen. <br />\r\n<br /><strong>Konstruktion:</strong><br />\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>40% Apex Neopren an den Schulter und Unterarmbahnen</li>\r\n<li>60% Dura Neopren im&nbsp; restlichen Anzug</li>\r\n<li>GBL Nähte<br />\r\n</li></ul><strong>Ausstattungsmerkmale:</strong><br />\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Charcoal Kontrast Naht</li>\r\n<li>Elastische Schlaufe für den Schlüssel an der inneren Rückenbahn</li>\r\n<li>Klettband zum leichteren Ziehen des Reißverschlusses</li>\r\n<li>TPU Knie Pads</li>\r\n<li>Cinch Loop Beinabschlüsse</li>\r\n<li>Abnehmbare Cinch Loop Beinabschlüsse&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Chromoplast Aufdruck</li></ul></div></div>', '<div class="product_title_big">\r\n<h2>NPX Vamp Semidry 5/4/3 GBL 2010</h2></div>\r\n<div class="product_text3">\r\n<div>Analogue to the cult for men, the "Vamp" is a reasonably prices wetsuit for women that anyway fits the NPX needs. The flashy design is perfect to address especially the younger generation.</div>\r\n<div><br />\r\n<strong>Design:</strong><br />\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>40% Apex Neoprene at the shoulders and the arm-beds</li>\r\n<li>60% Dura Neoprene at the rest of the suit</li>\r\n<li>GBL stitchings<br />\r\n</li></ul><strong>Fitting attributes:</strong><br />\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Charcoal contrast stitchings</li>\r\n<li>Elastic loop for the key at the inner back drapery</li>\r\n<li>Velcro for smooth zip drawing</li>\r\n<li>TPU knee pads</li>\r\n<li>Cinch Loop leg endings</li>\r\n<li>Removable Cinch Loop leg endings&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Chromoplast printing</li></ul></p></div></div>', '', '', '', 'wetsuit,suit,semidry,npx_,neoprene,vamp,2010', '', ''),
('adc920f4cbfa739803058c663a4a00b9', '<div class="product_title_big">\r\n<h2>Flyboards Flywave 2010</h2></div>\r\n<div class="product_text3"></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><strong>Form und Eigenschaften:</strong><br />\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>Dieses Board wurde in Zusammenarbeit mit dem niederländischen Wave-Guru Ruud Overwater entwickelt, und profitiert von mehr als 6 Jahren Erfahrung im Wellenreiten. Es ist vergleichsweise einfach im Handling und verleiht ein angenehmes Surfgefühl. Das Flywave ist besonders gut für kabbeliges Wasser und kurze Wellen geeignet. Ein Setup mit 3 Finnen (6cm) am Heck sowie 2 kleineren Finnen im Bugbereich sorgen für die nötige Stabilität. </div></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br /><strong>Konstruktion:</strong><br />\r\n</div></div></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>Der Kern des Flywave ist aus leichtem aber sehr langlebigem Paulownia Holz. Durch den Einsatz dieses Materials gehören gebrochene Boards der Vergangenheit an. Doppelt verstärkter Bug- und Heckbereich sowie Polyethylene-Schienen verleihen dem Board Stabilität und den nötigen Schutz. &nbsp; </div></div>\r\n<p>Insgesamt 18 Gewindeeinsätze sorgen für die optimale Standeinstellung auf dem Board, egal ob goofy, regular, straight oder wide.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><br />\r\n<strong>Details:</strong><br />\r\n<ul type="disc">\r\n<li class="MsoNormal">Größe: 145x39 cm</li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal">Gewicht: 3,06 kg<br />\r\n</li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal">Stand: 56cm - 60\r\ncm</li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal">Holz/Schaum-Kern</li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal">3x 6cm G10<br />\r\n  2x 4,5cm G10</li></ul></div></div></div></div>', '<div class="product_title_big">\r\n<h2>Flyboards Flywave 2010</h2></div>\r\n<div class="product_text3">\r\n<div><strong>The Shape and Characteristic:</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n   All new for 2010 is the addition of the FlyWave S to the Flyboards\r\nrange. Designed in association with Dutch wave-guru Ruud Overwater, who\r\nhas put over 6 years of wave riding experience into this board. The\r\nFlyWave S is a mutant style board for the rider who wants to ride the\r\nwaves powerful with a board that has a surf feeling, but still wants to\r\nkeep the advantages of a twin tip and is very easy to ride. The FlyWave S\r\n works really well in choppy and short waves (big or small), when\r\ntraditional surfboards are very uncomfortable. Flip nose and -tail are\r\nintegrated in the FlyWave S, creating a board that is very resistant to\r\nspray and is not prone to dive into a wave. The FlyWave has a 6cm\r\ntri-fin setup on the tail and two smaller fins at the nose, this way the\r\n board can still be ridden in both directions. The full wood core gives\r\nthe FlyWave S extreme durability; kite loops can now be performed\r\nwithout worries!<br />\r\n<br /><strong>Flex/Scoop-Rocker:</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n   The Scoop-Rocker line of the FlyWave is self adjusting from under- to overpowered conditions in parts of a second.<br />\r\n<br /><strong>Mutant Shape:</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n   With a pronounced riding feeling towards one side, due to the outline\r\n combined with the tri-fin setup the FlyWave S gives superb grip in the\r\nwaves. But still can be ridden in each direction, no jibing necessary!\r\nThe flat bottom creates a board that is fast and easy to ride, while the\r\n Flip nose and &#8211;tail give the FlyWave S comfort and control in waves and\r\n choppy conditions.<br />\r\n<br /><strong>The Construction:</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\n   The core of the FlyWave S is made out of light, but super durable\r\nPaulownia wood. Since Flyboards integrated this core material, broken\r\nboards have been a thing of the past.<br />\r\n   The inserts are double reinforced. Thin ABS rails and tips made out\r\nof polyethylene are used to protect the board and to increase the flex\r\nin the tips. Flyboards use a 3 Dimensional construction, to be able to\r\nadd the flex to the sides of the tips instead of only the whole tip. The\r\n weight of the FlyWave S will surprise you; it weighs almost the same as\r\n a FlyRadical M, giving you an even more enjoyable session on and off\r\nthe water!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n   With 18 inserts your optimum stance can always be created, whether it will be goofy, regular, straight or wide stance.<br />\r\n<br /><strong>Specs:</strong><br />\r\n<ul type="disc">\r\n<li class="MsoNormal">Size: 145x39 cm</li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal">Weight: 3,06 kg<br />\r\n</li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal">Stance: 56cm - 60\r\ncm</li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal">Wood/Foam Core</li>\r\n<li class="MsoNormal">3x 6cm G10<br />\r\n  2x 4,5cm G10</li></ul>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p></p></div></div>', '', '', 'kiteboard,kite,board,flywave,flyboards', 'kiteboard,kite,board,flywave,flyboards', '', ''),
('dc57391739360d306c8dfcb3a4295e19', '<div class="product_title_big">\r\n<h2>RRD Passion 2010 </h2></div>\r\n<div class="product_text3">\r\n<div>Dieser Kite überrascht total:\r\nStabil, kraftvoll und sehr einfach zu relaunchen sowie zu depowern!\r\nDieser Kite gibt jedem das Gefühl, dass er schon immer kiten konnte. Der\r\n neue Passion wurde komplett überarbeitet so dass seine Kraft und\r\nStabilität voll zur Geltung kommen.<br />\r\n<br /><strong>Eigenschaften:</strong><br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Stabilität</li>\r\n<li>Kraftvoll</li>\r\n<li>Leichte progressive Depower</li>\r\n<li>Mittlere/leichte Bar Druck</li>\r\n<li>SOFORTIGER Relaunch<br />\r\n</li></ul>\r\n<div><strong>Technologie:</strong></div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Neues SPS System mit einem neu entworfenen Ventil</li>\r\n<li>Leading Edge mit parallelen Nähten für maximale Haltbarkeit und geringere Dehnung</li>\r\n<li>heiß geklebtes Double Tape Liek</li>\r\n<li>PVC abgerundete Verstärkung an den Enden der Querstuts</li>\r\n<li>Metallic-PU verstärkte Quertube-Enden</li>\r\n<li>DP 175 LL Dacron</li>\r\n<li>Tejin T9600 Canopy</li>\r\n<li>Neu geformte Quertube-Protektoren</li>\r\n<li>Neue PVC-Ventilprotektoren<br />\r\n</li></ul><strong>Größen:</strong><br />\r\n<blockquote>   13.0 | 11.0 | 9.0 | 7.0 | 5.0 | 3.0<br />\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<div><strong>Lieferumfang:<br />\r\n</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Kite Passion</li>\r\n<li>Kitebag </li></ul></div></div></div>', '<div class="product_title_big">\r\n<h2>RRD Passion 2010 </h2></div>\r\n<div class="product_text3">\r\n<div>This kite totally surprises: stable, powerful and very easy to relaunch and to depower! This kite gives you the feeling that you have been able to kite all the time. The new Passion has completely been reworked so its power and stability shows to advantage.</div>\r\n<div><br />\r\n<strong>Properties:</strong><br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Stability</li>\r\n<li>Powerful</li>\r\n<li>Easy progressive depower</li>\r\n<li>Medium/easy bar pressure</li>\r\n<li>IMMEDIATE relaunch<br />\r\n</li></ul>\r\n<div><strong>Technology:</strong></div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>New SPS system with new developed valve</li>\r\n<li>Leading edge with parallel stitchings for maximum durability and low rotation</li>\r\n<li>Hot glued Double Tape Liek</li>\r\n<li>PVC rounded enforcement at the ends of the cross-stuts</li>\r\n<li>Metallic-PU enforced cross-tube ends</li>\r\n<li>DP 175 LL Dacron</li>\r\n<li>Tejin T9600 Canopy</li>\r\n<li>Newly formed cross tube protections</li>\r\n<li>New plastic valve protections<br />\r\n</li></ul><strong>Sizes:</strong><br />\r\n<blockquote>   13.0 | 11.0 | 9.0 | 7.0 | 5.0 | 3.0<br />\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<div><strong>Delivery:<br />\r\n</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Kite Passion</li>\r\n<li>Kite bag </li></ul></p></div></div></div>', '', '', 'kite,rrd_,passion,2010', 'kite,rrd_,passion,2010', '', ''),
